{"tid":1721102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講哂：中大學生留守，非中大手足應唔應該轉場其他地方幫手","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:09:29.000Z","uid":224095,"like":43,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"38f83d2fec0a62c7ad7e9b791fece8e5750a5e01","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"中大學生雖然似乎唔想攻出去，但會繼續block吐露港公路<br />\n<br />\n中大入面防禦措施已經尚算妥善建立，物資（除食物外）更加接近滿瀉。黑警即使要攻，以中大學生尚可守住一陣。<br />\n<br />\n反而外面其實黎明行動呢兩日開始接近樽頸位，一眾上班族已經慣左地鐵要等、馬路要塞，有公司開始安排Shuttle Bus，做唔到經濟停擺。其實極需要手足出去幫手。<br />\n<br />\n五毛分化黨可以死開，並唔係叫人棄守中大，而係作出更好既資源分配。<br />\n<br />\n轉場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留守 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feafa09e1818f922f5c52b049c2a98e433d8db78","tid":1721102,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3970cdced71a2c4df080a6a2fa00e13cacf0f40","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"550beedc2cdbdfdbb0ab628c45f19b98be8468c7","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"33f0b5c1a99b774edcefad91344912379c533027","tid":1721102,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"改善空間［左膠道德撚 唔係和理非］政治唔係你做啱嘅野就會贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719977</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99aed736287ca1e8feb7e61470bdb318b3798af6","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82f7ab3c4fe12c6852c37bbee068b5a0e484d531","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"冇人討論？"},{"pid":"cf5d95b509965c35cd8e12f1edfc3af43f9c8d5c","tid":1721102,"uid":291252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"b3a79ade69d415af5b9d785e5266ff3706a5b65e","tid":1721102,"uid":114801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"非中大人應該出番去開花<br />\n<br />\n久守太辛苦，戰戰兢兢令到人精神緊張。特別二號橋班前線"},{"pid":"8f6b322e055f9ef81115752e6174e3b435308e75","tid":1721102,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5b1801e79d51f0c485e0b81adffef67ddc7b450","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"200分敬意to 非中大前線<br />\n<br />\n但出黎啲task我覺得仲有意思"},{"pid":"8daae88e64db54ccaa1dcbbd56bf4a7e8e48eae2","tid":1721102,"uid":149849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:39:39.000Z","msg":"一陣又屌你話當人地condom啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e83e427b6b291dbc0e00f8a7e61d1621c69d2a7","tid":1721102,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"咪就係囉，根本好簡單，都唔知拗留唔留守做咩"},{"pid":"b2af65feff874466bcfded6ee56d05a9d1692053","tid":1721102,"uid":86672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"中大內部決定比較好<br />\n得佢地知入面實際人數<br />\n但唔建議分散太多人<br />\n其他地區有熱心市民（幫助）"},{"pid":"2b729005c84642b8944c4876c1906f983cb00198","tid":1721102,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"非中大人出去開花可以減輕基地資源負擔(食物、裝備同衛生)，中大人另一方面繼續研發工具同魔法，狗真係攻過嚟大家再嚟支援都未遲。"},{"pid":"e1aac4e00041a7637a86d385e1fd3be4cc6e432a","tid":1721102,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"宜家最大問題係<br />\n1:大量鬼肯定已經潛入<br />\n各大學入面嘅手足一旦被點相就仆街(esp煉金術師)<br />\n特別係長期留係入面相對戒心會低左<br />\n平日就話三五個鐘唔除罩.唔同人傾下計<br />\n一兩日時間100%包實太難<br />\n難聽講句入面每一個人都有可能係鬼<br />\n記者/司機/廚師/魔法師/上過訪問嘅<br />\n雖然不捉鬼但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2:ShittyU報左狗之後其他U嘅藍/紅學生/staff/prof都一定會逼管理層做野<br />\n當足夠多/上層人士比壓力嘅時候<br />\n校方無可能當睇唔到比你留係學校"},{"pid":"82a86ee434e9c352f623b55f4fdbe17e8907e8c8","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8daae88e64db54ccaa1dcbbd56bf4a7e8e48eae2","tid":1721102,"uid":149849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:39:39.000Z","msg":"一陣又屌你話當人地condom啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"呢個論點又係老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到好似前線冇中大學生浴血死守咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊有人當人係condom<br />\n<br />\n情感勒索有咩意思，大局觀戰術層面出發啦<br />\n而家事實係出面勇武唔夠，黎明行動開始缺乏力量唔能夠造成經濟停擺"},{"pid":"3951938e3b81830a18610ce77e04e477ee41943e","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"797584534aa7e0339044e355b1ac4248852dfcec","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"b93b2bed65e04a1d55ac476390bfad137b8d9cfa","tid":1721102,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"0a86425ca0da43d023a92135e54ae55ddebb6e81","tid":1721102,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"PLA 呀。"},{"pid":"14fcff45c50e7a52aaf4bf37a5ea281b51528013","tid":1721102,"uid":134628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:06:02.000Z","msg":"好撚憎人講condom論，前線手足見冇事就會轉場，洗你班人係到投票趕人走<br />\n你班暴大人咪撚淨係識係宿舍做軍師，有事先出嚟打個卡，物資又唔收又唔撚搬入城、又搞咩搜身當人係犯咁，枉班手足仆心仆命咁救你班大學生"},{"pid":"cb0d7077bd93c8b331025a1514ddff8482d6d344","tid":1721102,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"根本旁外人就唔撚洗比意見<br />\n中大守中大 絕無問題<br />\n不斷叫散水 不斷叫撒先最有問題"},{"pid":"5d2b8bf18b53a93ffc76576b46707e9daa7a8580","tid":1721102,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再防守，行動升級，人越多越安全<br />\n<br />\n10區警署要人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進攻係最好既防守<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他後備突擊方案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦<br />\n禮賓府<br />\n港交所<br />\n狗屋<br />\n狗宿舍</span></span>"},{"pid":"98a8e9bb5a3dda466ac7d63c3a6474bb563b7e4a","tid":1721102,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"雨革經驗黎講係應該<br />\n中大俾當年雨革佔中有個優勢<br />\n中大有廁所，有飯堂，有百佳！<br />\n中大可以係一個升lv據點<br />\n升完全部留係中大就冇左be water<br />\n狗都識be water，就證明表示哩個策略係可取<br />\n狗，宜家擺明做俾d市民睇淨係要橋，吐露港或者紅隧<br />\n佢地就係諗住不斷抹黑你地玩橋霸學府<br />\n等待出師有名ge時刻。<br />\nbe water做文宣，講解個大據點來源同功用<br />\n俾d支持我地ge師奶有圖片駁d姨媽姑姐先係有用！"}]}